<!-- The Big Vision -->
<div class="vision">
  <strong>🎯 End goal</strong> — one Omnara controlling your fleet of Omnara chats across all your machines.
  Tracker reads every session's metadata + content, exposes a single dashboard with TODOs / status / unread,
  routes "派活" requests to the right (machine, workspace) pair, and can auto-reply / escalate / kill on signals.
  Below is the full Omnara surface area I have access to with just <code>~/.omnara/creds.json</code>.
</div>

