report v2 generated by Claude · all data above pulled live from <code>api.omnara.com</code> with Steve's PAT · <a href="#" onclick="const r=document.getElementById('raw');r.style.display=r.style.display==='block'?'none':'block';return false">show embedded raw data ▾</a>
